@startuml Keyword Detection

title Keyword Detection

actor User
participant "Microphone" as MIC
participant "Vosk" as V
participant "MicrophoneListener" as ML
participant "KeywordDetector" as KD

== Keyword Detection ==

MIC -> ML : utterance complete
ML -> V : acceptWaveForm(buffer)
V --> ML : full transcript
ML -> KD : detect(transcript)
KD --> ML : keyword found
ML -> ML : enter recording mode clear commandBuffer
alt words follow keyword
    ML -> ML : append remainder to commandBuffer
end

@enduml
